icks-sporting.html&c=18103218871359343134&mkt=en-us","PublishTime":"6 hours ago","Source":"ismboard.com","Thumbnail":{"Height":393,"Url":"http:\/\/www.bing.com\/th?id=ON.03AC7D034FF07FBB201B80B7BCD2CD08&pid=News&sz=590x393","Width":590},"Title":"Canaccord Genuity Reaffirms \"Buy\" Rating for Dick's Sporting Goods Inc (DKS)","LtUpDtTm":"\/Date(-62104060800000+0000)\/","PbTmStp":"\/Date(-62104060800000+0000)\/","ProviderLogoUrl":null,"PublishTimeRaw":1.314539694E+17,"Snippet":"The Ohio-based James Investment Research Inc has invested 0.82% in the stock. About 254,811 shares traded. G-III Apparel Group, Ltd. (NASDAQ:GIII) has declined 47.99% since July 21, 2016 and is downtrending. It has underperformed by 4.31% the S&P500."},{"ArticleUrl":"http:\/\/www.bing.com\/news\/apiclick.aspx?ref=BDIGeneric&aid=5021FF6D1971DEF2E613F5DAD265192472D38E86&tid=28571B7BD15943119438C97707C30B1D&url=http%3a%2f%2fwww.alternet.org%2fnews-amp-politics%2ftrump-touts-made-america-week-indonesian-workers-toil-away-making-ivanka-trump&c=14825995347660095727&mkt=en-us","PublishTime":"3 days ago","Source":"Alter Net","Thumbnail":{"Height":100,"Url":"http:\/\/www.bing.com\/th?id=ON.4814621AB2DB70E0283F9F627C9E4FD8&pid=News&sz=100x100","Width":100},"Title":"As Trump Touts 'Made in America' Week, Indonesian Workers Toil Away Making Ivanka Trump Apparel","LtUpDtTm":"\/Date(-62104060800000+0000)\/","PbTmStp":"\/Date(-62104060800000+0000)\/","ProviderLogoUrl":null,"PublishTimeRaw":1.31451042E+17,"Snippet":"She talked about what she discovered in her investigation. KRITHIKA VARAGUR: I went to the factory in West Java, about three hours from Jakarta, that makes clothes for G-III Apparel Group, which is this global conglomerate that makes clothes for a bunch ..."},{"ArticleUrl":"http:\/\/www.bing.com\/news\/apiclick.aspx?ref=BDIGeneric&aid=5021FF6D1971DEF2E613F5DAD265192472D38E86&tid=28571B7BD15943119438C97707C30B1D&url=https%3a%2f%2fwww.bibeypost.com%2fglg-boosted-simon-ppty-group-new-spg-holding-by-671